Updates to the VOLS program from Gordon B. Hampton.

       email:  Gordon Boyd Hampton <gbhampton@yahoo.com>

11/26/08 11. UPDATED TO HANDLE OVER 9999 CYLS/DEVICE
             USING THE LSPACE MACRO

             OUTPUT KEYWORD PARAMETER ALLOWS
             EITHER OUT(30) OR OUT(40) FOR OUTPUT SIZE

             OUT(30) PRESENTS OLDER VERSION OUTPUT
               (FOR COMPATIBILITY - SHOWS 9999 FOR
                VALUES > 9999 AS OLD VERSION DOES)

             OUT(40) IS THE UPDATED LINE (40 BYTES)
               SOME FIELDS ARE BIGGER, SOME SHIFTED

             DEFAULT IS SET BY OUTPUT_SIZE VARIABLE
               FOR UPDATED VERSION DEFAULT, USE 40
               FOR OLDER VERSION DEFAULT CHANGE TO 30


